<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">各位考生：</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 37px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">我校<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">2023</span>年退役大学生士兵专升本职业技能测试成绩将于<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">3</span>月<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">14</span>日晚<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">7</span>点公布，现将成绩查询及有关事项通知如下：</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 37px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">一、查询方式</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 37px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">考生可在查询时间内登陆官网主页：<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">2023</span>年退役大学士兵专升本面试成绩查询入口，输入本人姓名和身份证号后六位进行查询。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 37px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">二、申请成绩复核</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 37px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">考生如对本人考试成绩有异议，可向我校教务处申请成绩复核，具体事项如下：</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 37px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">1.</span>填写《江西软件职业技术大学<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">2023</span>年退役大学生士兵专升本职业技能测试成绩复核申请表》，将《申请表》、第二代居民身份证的<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">PDF</span>扫描件电子稿（拍照必须清晰）发送至<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">363175498@qq.com</span>，材料不全的不予查询；</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 37px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">2.</span>申请查分时间：<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">2023</span>年<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">3</span>月<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">15</span>日<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">6:00-19</span>：<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">00</span>前（以发送电子邮件时间为准）；</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 37px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">3.</span>成绩复核工作将由我校教务处工作人员于<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">3</span>月<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">15</span>日集中进行，根据规定，成绩复核仅限于查核答卷是否漏改、漏统，如有漏改、漏统，予以更正。对于答题评分宽严等问题，不属于查核更正范围。复核过程中，答卷不与考生和家长见面。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 37px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">如考生成绩复查无误，我校将不予电话通知，如复查有误，<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">3</span>月<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">15</span>日<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">19</span>点前及时予以更正并电话通知考生本人。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 37px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">特此通知。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">附：江西软件职业技术大学<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">2023</span>年退役大学生士兵专升本职业技能测试成绩复核申请表<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">.doc</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">咨询电话：<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">0791-83792933</span></span></p><p draggable="true" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">联系人：张老师</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: right;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">江西软件职业技术大学大学教务处</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">2023</span>年<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">3</span>月<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">14</span>日</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);"><a href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/2023-03-14%2015%3A57%3A43%E6%B1%9F%E8%A5%BF%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E8%81%8C%E4%B8%9A%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%A62023%E5%B9%B4%E9%80%80%E5%BD%B9%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E5%A3%AB%E5%85%B5%E4%B8%93%E5%8D%87%E6%9C%AC%E8%81%8C%E4%B8%9A%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%E6%88%90%E7%BB%A9%E5%A4%8D%E6%A0%B8%E7%94%B3%E8%AF%B7%E8%A1%A8.docx?Expires=1994140663&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=ar6rNcq6ecbFB68U0wMg5o9zV2E%3D" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 0.3s ease-in 0s;">附件： 江西软件职业技术大学2023年退役大学生士兵专升职业技能测试成绩复核申请表</a></span></p><p><br/></p>